<%- include('./partials/header') %>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-5">About ElectroShop</h1>
      
      <div class="card mb-5">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title mb-4">Our Story</h2>
          <p>ElectroShop was founded in 2023 with a simple mission: to provide high-quality electronics at competitive prices with exceptional customer service. What began as a small online store has grown into a trusted destination for tech enthusiasts and everyday consumers alike.</p>
          <p>Our team consists of passionate tech experts who carefully curate our product selection to ensure we offer only the best devices and accessories on the market. We believe that technology should enhance your life, and we're here to help you find the perfect products to do just that.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card mb-5">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p>At ElectroShop, our mission is to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide a seamless shopping experience for all your electronics needs</li>
            <li>Offer a carefully selected range of high-quality products at competitive prices</li>
            <li>Deliver exceptional customer service before, during, and after your purchase</li>
            <li>Stay at the forefront of technology trends to bring you the latest innovations</li>
            <li>Build lasting relationships with our customers based on trust and satisfaction</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card mb-5">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title mb-4">Why Choose Us</h2>
          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary fa-2x me-3"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5>Quality Products</h5>
                  <p>We partner with trusted brands and rigorously test all products before adding them to our inventory.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <i class="fas fa-shipping-fast text-primary fa-2x me-3"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5>Fast Shipping</h5>
                  <p>We offer quick and reliable shipping options to get your products to you as soon as possible.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <i class="fas fa-headset text-primary fa-2x me-3"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5>Customer Support</h5>
                  <p>Our dedicated support team is always ready to assist you with any questions or concerns.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <i class="fas fa-undo text-primary fa-2x me-3"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5>Easy Returns</h5>
                  <p>We offer a hassle-free return policy because we stand behind the quality of our products.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title mb-4">Our Team</h2>
          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
              <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="Team Member">
              <h5>John Doe</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">Founder & CEO</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
              <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="Team Member">
              <h5>Jane Smith</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">CTO</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
              <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="Team Member">
              <h5>Mike Johnson</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">Head of Customer Service</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

